title: Sweet Potato Frittata
ingredients: ['1 red pepper, seeded and chopped into 2cm pieces', '1 medium size sweet potato, chopped into 2cm pieces', '60g baby spinach leaves', '6 free range eggs', '2 cloves garlic', '125ml milk', '115g grated Cheddar cheese', '1 small onion, chopped into 2cm pieces', 'olive oil for frying']
